{"tid":1043975,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[轉貼] Mercedes-AMG A 45 確定輸出 383 匹及 416 匹馬力","createTime":"2019-03-02T15:18:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T08:17:36.000Z","uid":111872,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2fd160934b63cae8fe818e1047585032998f7918","tid":1043975,"uid":111872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T15:18:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lrbdDLwkevo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlrbdDLwkevo&d=Xug72IqGonTeMs94ciZuWoV%2FGdaNkEJkjxlYCjQUfm8%3D&h=d949b052\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lrbdDLwkevo</a><br />\n<br />\n估完又再估，講了又再講，如今，終於確定了 Mercedes-AMG A45 的動力數據資料了！Mercedes-Benz 邀請汽車 YouTuber Shmee150 到瑞典參加全新 Mercedes-AMG A45 活動。在影中確認了新一代 AMG A45 的馬力為 383 匹馬力，而更強的 AMG A45 S 馬力則為 416 匹！據了解，AMG A45 雖然是以前驅平台打造，但四驅系統卻配備了十分高科技系統，每個車輪內都有單獨的離合器，令到扭力能夠更快速分配，甚至可以將 100% 動力傳送至單輪上，當然車子的系統會因應循跡性、車身角度和轉向角等多方面資訊進行傳送比例。另外，AMG A45 配備了漂移模式，而在影片中就需要進行操作才能打開漂移模式，首先切換為 Race 模式，關閉 ESP 系統，再同時拉兩個換檔撥片，再拉右側撥片，然後在儀錶板上出現「Drift」後就可盡情漂移了！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.car1.hk/news/mercedes-amg-a45-determines-output-of-383-horsepower-and-416-horsepower/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.car1.hk%2Fnews%2Fmercedes-amg-a45-determines-output-of-383-horsepower-and-416-horsepower%2F&d=Xug72IqGonTeMs94ciZuWoV%2FGdaNkEJkjxlYCjQUfm8%3D&h=e17ce7e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.car1.hk/news/mercedes-amg-a45-determines-output-of-383-horsepower-and-416-horsepower/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n100% 單輪動力，Drift Mode<br />\n抄Focus RS 抄到十足<br />\n<br />\n新出S 版 去到416 匹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1772d652799a94c72139955b25ffa6d3f4c50e1","tid":1043975,"uid":65658,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T15:51:45.000Z","msg":"痴撚線hatchback 400幾匹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇返十幾年前f360先得400匹"},{"pid":"84531e88eebd3db927c659708bd6226d512e0acd